{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"getting-started\"><a href=\"#getting-started\" aria-label=\"getting started permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting Started!</h1>\n<h2 id=\"about-flame\"><a href=\"#about-flame\" aria-label=\"about flame permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>About Flame</h2>\n<p>Flame is a minimalist Flutter game engine built on top of <a href=\"https://flutter.dev/\">Flutter</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"goals\"><a href=\"#goals\" aria-label=\"goals permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Goals</h2>\n<p>The goal of this project is to provided a complete set of out-of-the-way solutions for the common problems every game developed in Flutter will share.\nCurrently it provides you with: a few utilities, images/sprites/sprite sheets, audio, a game loop and a component/object system.</p>\n<p>You can use whatever ones you want, as they are all somewhat independent.</p>\n<h2 id=\"learning-resources\"><a href=\"#learning-resources\" aria-label=\"learning resources permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Learning resources</h2>\n<p>The community has created some articles and examples of a good usage of Flame.</p>\n<p>Check out this great series of articles/tutorials written by <a href=\"https://github.com/japalekhin\">Alekhin</a>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/create-mobile-game-flutter-flame-beginner-tutorial\">Create a Mobile Game with Flutter and Flame – Beginner Tutorial (Part 0 of 5)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/2d-casual-mobile-game-tutorial-flame-flutter-part-1\">2D Casual Mobile Game Tutorial – Step by Step with Flame and Flutter (Part 1 of 5)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/game-graphics-and-animation-tutorial-flame-flutter-part-2\">Game Graphics and Animation Tutorial – Step by Step with Flame and Flutter (Part 2 of 5)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/views-dialog-boxes-tutorial-flame-flutter-part-3\">Views and Dialog Boxes Tutorial – Step by Step with Flame and Flutter (Part 3 of 5)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/scoring-storage-sound-tutorial-flame-flutter-part-4\">Scoring, Storage, and Sound Tutorial – Step by Step with Flame and Flutter (Part 4 of 5)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jap.alekhin.io/game-finishing-packaging-tutorial-flame-flutter-part-5\">Game Finishing and Packaging Tutorial – Step by Step with Flame and Flutter (Part 5 of 5)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p>Put the pub package as your dependency by dropping the following in your <code class=\"language-text\">pubspec.yaml</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">dependencies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">flame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ^0.17.0</code></pre></div>\n<p>And start using it!</p>\n<h2 id=\"topics\"><a href=\"#topics\" aria-label=\"topics permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Topics</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Core Concepts</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/structure.md\">Structure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/game.md\">Game Loop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/components.md\">Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/input.md\">Input</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Audio</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/audio.md\">General Audio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/bgm.md\">Looping Background Music</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Rendering</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/images.md\">Images, Sprites and Animations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/text.md\">Text Rendering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/palette.md\">Colors and the Palette</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Other Modules</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/util.md\">Util</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/gamepad.md\">Gamepad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/box2d.md\">Box2D</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/tiled.md\">Tiled</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/debug.md\">Debugging</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/docs/","title":"Getting Started"}}},"pageContext":{}}